==English==

===Etymology===
From the similarity of the stripes to those of a [[zebra]].

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[zebra]] [[crossing]]}}

# A [[pedestrian crossing]] featuring broad white [[stripe]]s painted parallel to the street.

